text: Md. Saifur Rahman is a Bangladeshi politician for the Jatiya Party (Ershad), a former Member of Parliament in the Dhaka-3 constituency. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Dhaka-3 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:1951 births
title: Md. Saifur Rahman
